{"tid":1685014,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當全面禁網 郭文貴條粉腸就會係海外騎劫香港示威運動 散播假新聞","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T02:52:59.000Z","uid":103618,"like":81,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fec04489c22b8c3befc4d7f9eaf87b2f0400eb","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"【借Post】【討論Post大家發表下意見】<br />\nTL;DR: <br />\n1) 郭文貴係香港影響力~0， 但係海外大把岩岩覺醒／不明真相既大陸人、海外華人信晒佢<br />\n2) 睇番郭文貴之前一直表面上反共，實際上響應共產黨言論的行為，有理由懷疑人地係共產黨個邊既人，幫手掌握海外反共勢力（詳情大家睇內文再判斷啦）<br />\n3) 如果香港真係禁晒網，比佢「代港出聲」Connect海外，甘就死得<br />\n4) 大家睇晒篇野後再搵下佢最新既各種9up野，重新思考下佢對我地既實際威脅啦<br />\n<br />\n詳細版本（代有心既覺醒人士轉載）<br />\n國內和海外有很多反共人士，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">郭文貴一直在營造他是香港這場運動的推動者的形象</span></span>，好吸收這些反共人士的關注，但是實際上是希望擴大他個人的影響力好進行金錢詐騙。<br />\n<br />\n由六月開始郭文貴一直通過製造解放軍戒嚴、大開殺戒等謠言來製造熱度，吸引眼球，然後通過他的粉絲平台的散播來擴大影響，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經吸引了不少支持香港但不明真相的大陸人、台灣人和海外華人、甚至是香港人</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n在十月初開始編造他是香港人五大訴求的倡導人角色，同時編造他支持了香港抗爭者300萬美金和一批裝備的謊言，繼續造謠撞騙，實質目的就是為了吸收同情香港的人士的捐款。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們希望民間記者會能澄清事實，反擊這種蹭香港熱度騎劫香港抗爭運動的騙子。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求是七月一日香港抗爭者提出的，為什麼郭文貴不在那時說五大訴求是他倡導的而是等到十月四日直播才說出來，因為他看到港共出台緊急法，未來香港可能會封網滅聲這個騎劫香港抗爭運動的機會，所以才選擇著這個時候說出來，利用港共的配合達到徹底騎劫香港這場運動的目的，所以這個事一定要民間記者會澄清才能徹底阻止郭文貴騎劫這場運動的企圖。<br />\n<br />\n這幾年由郭在海外做的事來看，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他很大可能就是習派到海外的大外宣</span></span>，因為在台灣選舉上他一直通過各種手段黑共產黨不喜歡的蔡英文總統，在海外利用美國的法院纏訴海外民運份子中有漏洞的幾個人來攪亂整個海外民運勢力，這些事雖然在反共口號下做的隱蔽但是還是露出了馬腳，所以揭穿他才能徹底破壞共產黨在海外宣傳，同時避免未來共產黨倒台以後利用海外勢力借屍還魂的可能。這是一個非常重要的事情，不能無視<br />\n<br />\n我們做了一個PDF的說明和剪輯了兩個視頻，他的這些言詞對哪些不太了解情況的人非常有鼓動性，比如他說美國前三位領導人打電話給他，如果不細想其實美國前三位領導人川普、彭斯都沒留小鬍子，而第三位南希.佩洛西是女人，更不有可能有鬍子，不注意就被矇騙了<br />\n<br />\n所以這個共黨騙子危害極大，並逐步向美國政界和輿論屆滲透中，如果被他騎劫成功，未來香港的西方話事權他能控制不少，所以請民間記者會及時澄清事實，揭穿他的謊言。<br />\n<br />\n我們剪輯的視頻因為時間關係，只是他的油管ID郭文貴發布的視頻中的很小一部分，PDF文件有詳細出處鏈接和時間點的備註，供你們進行核對，剪輯的視頻和PDF文件都在這個網路文件夾裡面，你們可以下載後隨意修改。<br />\n<br />\n視頻剪輯常用谷歌☁文件夾<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1SKFUskSR1HaB7F2x8oTo26pc7c577pEw?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1SKFUskSR1HaB7F2x8oTo26pc7c577pEw%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=10a4b1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1SKFUskSR1HaB7F2x8oTo26pc7c577pEw?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴視頻中提到的郭媒體（Guo.Media）是由其實際控制的香港金泉公司名下的，對於一個如此高調反共的人，金泉公司仍沒有被中共關閉，裡面的內幕關係大家可想而知，而郭本人的其它公司都是因為經濟案件，比如洗錢案等被凍結帳戶和公司。<br />\n<br />\n你問問他們郭文貴為什麼要美國調查公司去調查受美國政府保護的15個給美國政府提供了幫助外國人（包括中國人）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tanghan32967114/status/1165270412718034945?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftanghan32967114%2Fstatus%2F1165270412718034945%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=b530e8d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftanghan32967114%2Fstatus%2F1165270412718034945%3Fs%3D21&h=2eab16f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tanghan32967114/status/1165270412718034945?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tanghan32967114/status/1153927150229045249?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftanghan32967114%2Fstatus%2F1153927150229045249%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=a9d60fef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftanghan32967114%2Fstatus%2F1153927150229045249%3Fs%3D21&h=7f21f2f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tanghan32967114/status/1153927150229045249?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n問問他們郭文貴兌現了這些所謂爆料沒有？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1150411409554980864?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1150411409554980864%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8fde8e09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1150411409554980864%3Fs%3D21&h=59891b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1150411409554980864?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1122523871104524289?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1122523871104524289%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=20554d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1122523871104524289%3Fs%3D21&h=91a0cc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1122523871104524289?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n看看這個騙子什麼智商，標籤上寫著2017年生產，他說他1994年買的，還幾百箱<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1122523871104524289?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1122523871104524289%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=20554d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjianwuaus%2Fstatus%2F1122523871104524289%3Fs%3D21&h=91a0cc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jianwuaus/status/1122523871104524289?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n看這個詐騙犯怎麼造謠的，問問他們有沒有一個國家能拿到政治庇護，包括郭文貴現在申請政治庇護美國給了沒有？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charlesguo9/status/1121129905943662592?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharlesguo9%2Fstatus%2F1121129905943662592%3Fs%3D21&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=fd2ec4a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharlesguo9%2Fstatus%2F1121129905943662592%3Fs%3D21&h=4e2a24ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charlesguo9/status/1121129905943662592?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"35e9e4515e97c87b84feacae9a0ecb35c987d6d4","tid":1685014,"uid":252064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROQsR9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROQsR9E.jpg&h=97363192&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d6d0fb4656d895b55e3f00f38868b16b72e79c0","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"b25c2872e40e3c851cc634bea05e52a34bae9b18","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"12ba4d256238ad1dfd07c110bc4b6aafe242d67c","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"eccd5e3d6b8f455c66e8c45b7ff0f88c53c2ad69","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"8c0c9696a06d24ca16f0765029aa86c1a1fcaf3e","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"24082c24218e176ae0acf8abbde517c6623040b1","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"3004e4c3fa872d9c7c63e7616761bc086eaaaacd","tid":1685014,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe95b16cb416bccc7b18c79c9124b7123c8e11c9","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"95fc7cb3aa27114acb83661ef9b772e0a9669b71","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"68f668ddbe009f42410ce459af714bafbc7dcb16","tid":1685014,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"